doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    - var name = 'Home'
    - var special = 1
    - var vacation = 0
    title BruTech Computer - Test Page
    link(rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/images/favicon.ico")
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="assets/styles/main.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="assets/styles/navbar.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="assets/styles/services.css")
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    script(src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/83100d2143.js" crossorigin="anonymous")
    body.background-graphic(data-bs-spy="scroll" data-bs-target="#myNavbar" data-bs-offset="0" tabindex="0")
      nav#myNavbar.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.border-bottom.fixed-top(style="background-color: #bdccfc;")
        div.container
          a.navbar-brand(href="index.html")
            img(
              src="assets/images/BT_Logo.png"
              height="50px"
            )
          ul.navbar-nav.nav-pills
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="index.html#home") Home
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="index.html#services") Services
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="index.html#about") About
            
      container#home
        div.py-5.my-5.text-center
          <marquee width="60%" bgcolor="red" font style="bold" scrolldelay="100"><font size="5" face="Verdana"><font color="White">*** Computer running slow?  We can fix it for much less than a new computer! ***</marquee>
          <marquee width="60%" bgcolor="#00ba00" font style="bold" scrolldelay="100"><font size="5" face="Verdana"><font color="White">*** We will be closed Friday mm/dd thru Monday mm/dd.  Please leave us a message and we will get back to you as soon as we get back. ***</marquee>
          img.d-block.mx-auto.mb-0.pb-0(src="assets/images/BruTech_Logo.png" alt="BruTech Computer logo")
          h3.px-0.py-0.pt-0.pb-3 For all your technology needs
          div
            table(style="width:100%", border="0")
              tr
                td.px-3(style="vertical-align:top; text-align:right", width="20%")
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Hours:
                td(style="vertical-align:top; text-align:left", width="15%")
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 M-F 9am-5pm
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Sat Appt Only
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Sun Closed
                td(style="vertical-align:top; text-align:center", width="30%")
                  h2.text-blue.pt-0.pb-0.color-green (682) 498-3377
                td.px-3(style="vertical-align:top; text-align:right", width="15%")
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Service Areas:
                td(style="vertical-align:top; text-align:left", width="20")
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Pecan
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 DeCordova
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Granbury
                  h5.pt-0.pb-0 Glen Rose
            div.d-grid.gap-2.d-sm-flex.justify-content-sm-center
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-4.gap-3(type="button" href="index.html%home") Home
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-4.gap-3(type="button" href="index.html#services") Services
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-4.gap-3(type="button" href="index.html#about") About

      container#services
        div.container

          h2.card-icon-blue Services
          hr

          div.card.mb-3.card-service
            div.row.g-0
              div.col-md-4.text-center.align-items-center.py-5.px-4
                  img(src="assets/images/PC_Tune_Up_Image.jpg" alt="")
              div.col-md-8.card-content-left
                div.card-body
                  h5.card-title.card-title-green PC Tune Up
                  ul.card-text
                    li Is your computer safe?
                    li Do you have malware stealing your information?
                    li Is your computer up to date?
                    li Are you running efficiently?

          div.card.mb-3.me-0.ms-auto.card-service
            div.row.g-0
              div.col-md-8.card-content-right
                div.card-body
                  h5.card-title.card-title-green Diagnostics
                  ul.card-text 
                    li Something not working right?
                    li Computer running slow?
                    li Computer not turning off or on?
              div.col-md-4.text-center.align-items-center.py-5.px-4
                  img(src="assets/images/PC_Diagnostics_Image.jpg" alt="")

          div.card.mb-3.card-service
            div.row.g-0
              div.col-md-4.text-center.align-items-center.py-5.px-4
                  img(src="assets/images/PC_Upgrade_Image.jpg" alt="")
              div.col-md-8.card-content-left
                div.card-body
                  h5.card-title.card-title-green PC Upgrade
                  ul.card-text
                    li Need more storage?
                    li Additional memory?
                    li New printer?
                    li Home network?

          div.card.mb-3.me-0.ms-auto.card-service
            div.row.g-0
              div.col-md-8.card-content-right
                div.card-body
                  h5.card-title.card-title-green Remote Support or Pick Up/Drop Off
                  ul.card-text
                    li Need help from afar?
                    li Don't want to leave your home for help?
                    li Too busy?
              div.col-md-4.text-center.align-items-center.py-5.px-4
                  img(src="assets/images/PC_Remote_Image.jpg" alt="")

      container#about
        div.px-4.pt-5.pb-0.my-5.text-center.card-icon-blue
          h1 About BruTech Computer
        div.pt-0.pb-2.text-about
          h5
            p.
              I live in Pecan Plantation with my wife, Yvonne, and two small dogs.  When we are not remodeling the house, we are attempting to chisel away at our golf handicaps, so far with modest success.
            p. 
              I have worked on nearly everything in personal technology; computer hardware and software; programming; home networks; phone equipment; mobile; security systems; and home automation.
            p.
              I began my interests in computers and technology at the age of 15.  I started my first business while still in college pursuing a computer science degree.  After selling that business seven years later, I was hired as the lead Information Technology Technician at Western Washington University.  After 16 years, I moved on as the Information Technology Manager for a large Heavy Industrial Construction company.
            p.
              Now wanting to be closer to family, and better weather, I have once again started my own business.
            p.
              My goal is to use my 35 years of computer experience to assist my clients in all their technology needs.  I hope to help you enjoy technology as much as I do, or at least make yours work better.

      container#footer
        footer.d-flex.flex-wrap.justify-content-between.align-items-center.py-3.my-4.border-top.container-fluid(style="background-color: #bdccfc;")
          p.col-md-4.mb-0.text-muted Â© 2022-2024 BruTech Computer (Developed by Nick & Dan Brunner)

          a.col-md-4.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.mb-3.mb-md-0.me-md-auto.link-light.text-decoration-none(href="index.html")
              img(src="assets/images/BT_Logo.png" height="50px")

          ul.nav.col-md-4.justify-content-end
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href="index.html#home") Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href="index.html#services") Services
            if name.toLowerCase() !== "about"
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href="index.html#about") About

